text: Nocardioides caeni is a gram-positive and non-motile bacterium from the genus Nocardioides that has been isolated from sludge from domestic wastewater in Daejeon, South Korea.UniProtDeutsche Sammlung von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen == References == ==External links== *Type strain of Nocardioides caeni at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase caeni Category:Bacteria described in 2009
